longBusinessSummary: Cassius Ventures Ltd., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Canada. It focuses on the exploration of gold and other precious metals deposits. Cassius Ventures Ltd. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
